data.title: Registration Districts in Tyne & Wear
data.meta_description: Registration District information for Tyne & Wear
data.text:
The list below shows the civil registration districts in Tyne & Wear since 1974.

For the purposes of these pages, "Tyne & Wear" refers to the metropolitan county of that name, which was formed on 1.4.1974 out of the counties of Northumberland and Durham.

Click on a district name in the table below to see the places and dates covered, or see the Index of Place Names for the whole of England and Wales.
